{"tid":680489,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日咁熱都有人出黎平反六四，顯示建設民主中國先係正路。","createTime":"2018-05-27T08:31:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T09:37:22.000Z","uid":2429,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b0b09e024fe3ebebd64945eeee625d4743c2d024","tid":680489,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:31:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1398426-20180527.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1398426-20180527.htm&d=ScJHb5btZNdrEc9xxEec%2Fu9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=30a0774b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1398426-20180527.htm&h=84269257\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1398426-20180527.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n支聯會發起遊行，悼念六四事件29周年，主席何俊仁表示，支聯會一向堅信及堅持五大綱領。他說，支聯會的長遠願景，就是爭取民主中國，因此必須要結束一黨專政，遊行中會清楚聽到有關口號，他強調叫口號屬於言論自由。 遊行隊伍下午3時許由灣仔修頓球場出發，終點為中聯辦，警方開放一條行車線。遊行開始前，大會先在球場集會，現場有人手持「平反六四」及「建設民主中國」等標語。 副主席蔡耀昌發表遊行宣言，他表示，現時叫口號的代價愈來愈大，又帶領參與市民高叫「結束一黨專政」等口號。 <br />\n<br />\n有無手足一齊去維園晚會捐錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091373fbf83a801e3a4762f685f02e1727da2b20","tid":680489,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:33:18.000Z","msg":"平反六四 以死相搏"},{"pid":"7f9e802d38aa8606182e8d73bc666ff3f1d14556","tid":680489,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:30:07.000Z","msg":"去大灣區慢慢建設<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b37219327a3b0a4926fc1d915bac60d2f979603d","tid":680489,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:37:22.000Z","msg":"建設中屬香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}